@node "Main" "PatchOverscan"

PatchOverscan should run under WB 2.1 or higher. (NOT TESTED!)

This Program has been tested under WB 40.42/KS 40.68 (OS3.1)
on an A4000/EC030 with 10 MB RAM and on an A1200/030.
Compiled with SAS/C 6.56.
Thanx to SAS people for such a good compiler.

Written by Thomas Krafzik in 1995/96.
This is FREEWARE.
All Rights reserved worldwide.

